snippet.textDisplay:
This song has such a strong message about fear of uncertainty. "What if I don't find joy in this thing that I used to love?" is terrifying, and knowing about their career as creators is even more heartbreaking from the point of view of a fan.
I found my first death many years ago, so this song makes me cry so hard, truly cry. Not finding joy or not being able to do something that you loved with all your heart, knowing that the time has passed [as in "what if the moment is right now"] and you can't have it back...


I think this is my favorite song and MV of all.
